Package: gggda
Type: Package
Title: Geometric Data Analysis Layers for 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Jason Cory",
           family = "Brunson",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "cornelioid@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3126-9494")))
Description: Geometric data analysis (GDA) comprises multivariate techniques
    based on geometric concepts and physical principles.
    Le Roux & Rouanet (2005) <doi:10.1007/1-4020-2236-0> provide a thorough
    introduction.
    This package provides common GDA plotting elements for Wickham's (2010)
    <doi:10.1198/jcgs.2009.07098> layered grammar of graphics.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.0),
    ggplot2
